                ["body"] = "<p><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/728x200_版本维护更新说明.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></p>\n<p>亲爱的狩月人：<br>感谢您的关注与支持，以下是华胥资料片「大风歌&middot;下」2026年2月10日版本更新说明，辛苦查阅。</p>\n<div data-page-id=\"Q6WFdgAUloUjB9xhSB3cv0cwnUe\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnJ6IGmLDYnhE7sHC38ZgAxe\">✦维护更新说明✦</h3>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnqxN6l6hUrIQYfVqruHCxWe\"><strong>◆维护时间◆</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn3WILWbhezGlT5oOr8ZZARc\">2026年2月10日（星期二）04:00-11:00（UTC+8）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnA91v2r0N0WMCwmMgtkBQrg\">*开服时间视维护进度有可能提前或推迟，还请留意公告通知。维护更新期间所有服务器将无法登录，请狩月人合理安排游戏时间。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnDVt9lJcvQm9Q825DdNcDnc\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-doxcn44BOooW7zUgZYekZOLYZgb\"><strong>◆维护补偿◆</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnk2dtWdYboPeHwnMAt4B7Xe\">月石*300、委托手册&middot;二*6、委托手册&middot;三*4、玩具气锤*10、消耗物品【千丝雨&middot;鎏金】*3</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnPE3w85qUFdldwu2M4tHHK4\">* 领取条件：解锁【邮件】功能，邮件领取有效时间至2026年2月17日23:59（UTC+8）。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-X129dMk11o579XxS1Bmc0Xxkn5g\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-IkHmdrqyHowZtYxa6i1cjMmlnAb\"><strong>◆活动下架提醒◆</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-DUWod4EbnoX8FUxHgzNcvLNZnQd\">以下商品将于2026年2月10日 4:00（UTC+8）优惠期限到期或下架。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-BdTZdLhHfoWbxUxKkoscY8ydnkb\">●「狩月人形象礼箱&middot;墨玉」、「闻香自选形象礼箱&middot;墨玉」、「奇思喵想」系列、「星河盛放」优惠价将于2026年2月10日 4:00（UTC+8）结束。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-XdtTdjzgiouDgZxbJxrcUliBnDK\">●「潮音万华礼箱」系列、「香韵万华礼箱」系列、「思绪礼箱&middot;刻舟」、「交织的思绪&middot;刻舟」、「外观组合礼箱&middot;星芒」、「粼粼水波」系列、「烛阴」系列、「星霜」系列、「兔玲珑」系列将于2026年2月10日 4:00（UTC+8）下架。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-YclXd7Ff6oJP0exxd9wcjGwQnce\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-YH1nd4hhDotYfkxW7g0cEvlsnXb\">以下活动将于2026年2月10日 4:00（UTC+8）结束，各位狩月人请记得及时领取活动中的奖励。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-S2hXdyXaLoj8HVxysBNcGF1DnyW\">● 活动限定万华【潮音起天末】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HlNsdk4atobhiMxxTk2cgLASnff\">● 时装试玩【水色吐息】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GfgOdIEQTod11xxhfg3cVB6FnSh\">● 吟游诗集【烟津闻弦II】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-T0hSdRUBaocVuNxcHBAc5qKsnC3\">● 角色试玩【沙痕留迹】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HQjRdOr8eo67cSxNNb8cm0Tqnne\">● 其他活动【轰鸣演练】【沉浸式戏剧-刻舟】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CFIjdvhX2oFnBgxwyxbcsquOnLh\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-IhNfdh5eEoUPogxWktCcXjGrnPb\">在活动限定万华【潮音起天末】结束后，当期可兑换商品将于2026年2月16日 05:00下架。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KPrAdxs5MoG3A5xG4V5cuZ8Snbf\">● 扶疏形象「素浪濯心」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HQdrdIN6ZoH3dpxQIuwcmDQknpe\">● 武器形象「大浪淘鲨」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VvU1d0EBFogBZGxdkpFc7ERxnDc\">● 展示动作「悠游水岸」系列、「泡泡泡泡鸭」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CHqgdLTjsoGUrpxJSCQcZuD4n4g\">● 武器装饰「趴趴海星」系列、「缤纷海螺」系列</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-S2hndUp4loGlUzxx52GcCyhan7I\">● 头部装饰「真夏墨镜」系列、光晕「鱼影清歌」系列</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-MMHxdZf8goacg0xqra3cSdzEnKg\">● 足迹特效「小鸭力」系列</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Js8fdxxAnoneTJxLBYJcdPuAn2e\">● 螺旋飞跃特效「凌波疾步」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PwDAdUNreolovOx2ZXOcrwT8nY6\">● 下落攻击特效「种一个夏日」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-I4mXdt07lownsIxABFIcUDNfnDd\">● 传送特效「星云幻境」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HgkUdPkf9o868exJw8EclJe7nze\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZjEvdaF7QoMAvxxKuSBcFqPMn6d\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnpss4nWdinxGyUQGvpbvXJh\"><strong>◆更新方式◆</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-YjnidW9TooLJhUxqnmocZoShnjb\">PC端：重新开启启动器后，点击【更新游戏】，进行更新；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-XBB4dzXCpoczPpxKLaTclkHAnXc\">安卓端：进入游戏后，根据游戏弹窗提示进行更新；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-O9pwdHYmloqxk9xhfAlcK7zGnNe\">iOS端：前往App Store进行更新。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnLvxLwDXabNX93mPi23qf9b\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-doxcndWk5Gq8XP9zYyYmCI6jeQd\"><strong>◆设备要求◆</strong></h3>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-BlGMdz9IAo6pVoxCBHscXlsen76\">为保证游戏的顺利安装与体验，建议狩月人参考以下配置要求：</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-El7CdSxPKoWJGExeUIJcobfPn8g\"><strong>最低配置</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Gf3YdWwYsoOwTqx6LnmcwrwynHe\">Android：系统Android 8及以上、处理器高通骁龙 845/天玑1000以上、运行内存8GB以上、可用存储空间20GB以上；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Dzmad9xUGogGTKxIbyucuUKNnjg\">iOS：iPhone 12以上型号、系统版本iOS 15.0以上、可用存储空间20G以上；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-BZ4Md6IOEosDoYxUOQacL9mynOb\">可用存储空间：20GB以上；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-YQbpd30G3oNLFyxxU4Hcyj9kn7b\">PC：系统Windows 10 64bit以上、处理器Intel Core i5(第九代) /AMD Ryzen 5 2600X以上、显卡Geforce GTX1060/AMD Radeon RX 580以上、运行内存16GB以上、可用存储空间40G以上。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RrLHd4DtKoyN61xybqYcSrSonGg\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-YDBBdHpF8ocKVUxANHHc4iAtnJb\"><strong>推荐配置</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ByKydkGpfohTAAxLgTccy7nbnbf\">Android：系统Android 12、处理器高通骁龙 8Gen 1/ 天玑 9000、内存12GB 以上、可用存储空间20GB 以上；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-NsFldwM5cobZyGxXVJxctwaQnab\">iOS：机型iPhone 14 Pro、系统iOS 17.0、可用存储空间20GB及以上；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-R0IJd4JLRo93CAxIxa8cWW4gnSf\">PC：系统Windows 10 64bit、处理器:Intel core i7(第十代)/AMD Ryzen 7 3700x、显卡GeForce RTX 2060/AMD Radeon RX5700XT、运行内存32GB及以上、预留硬盘空间：40GB及以上。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RgUIdDC58owWlDxuy2XcjvWCnRd\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ItJ3dSDpRoaJnZxy1xxcUCtpnlg\"><strong>手柄支持</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-XKLidS372ohsd6x38dqcDGgmn6b\">目前《二重螺旋》于PC设备支持以下有线/无线控制器。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JTSid0uzSoIA07xUAubcDJoqnSd\">Xbox：Xbox系列、Xbox Elite系列</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HYhWdoZxVodyerxEOz9cTf8fnqf\">Playstation&reg;：DualSense&reg;、DualSense Edge&trade;、DUALSHOCK&reg;4</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ADZqdGaLAoKywVxyGIDcOYUEnzf\">*使用DualSense&reg;或DUALSHOCK&reg;4控制器在PC端进行体验时，推荐您采用有线连接方式以获得最佳游玩体验。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RUkZdI1z6ogIAbx1HO5cfr7znDb\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnMxMeInESZOTm0pTYqkjGVh\"><strong>✦版本全新内容 ✦</strong></h3>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-AtVzdyKhqoswqJxhWZMc17YlnAh\"><strong>◆全新剧情任务开放◆</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZFmmdluL9oBlqpx2T4xc9ubmnDe\">烟津渡的日与夜，在茶摊的交谈声、码头的吆喝声、孩子的笑语中缓缓流转。每一缕清风都捎来一段未诉尽的人间烟火。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-DjNbdqktYoG9B6xNDCvceTthnCI\">新增支线剧情「错时重逢」、「高光时刻」、「闹鬼妙妙香」、「香火归尘」、「虬先生的投资」、「花茶的味道」、「烟津渡最大危机！」、「梨与礼」、「柳色如故」；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-L2gmdZytiolnZ5x0ghjcIkd1nkc\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnpsv0EAMzRcdxOdAdrmTN4g\"><strong>◆全新角色◆</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-AKUYd3D9Po5Ty4xqDJrc9Z8pnKf\">雷属性&middot;「止流」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CkG5dMKayo7NN4xg655c6cNanSh\">✦ 武器精通：重剑/双枪</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-MNibdj8N6ogKdKxq6aRchpVHnEe\">✦ 获取开放时间：2月10日（UTC+8）更新后长期开放；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JNLJdrBPPo7B8hxqpkNcdBAUnTh\">✦ 获取方式：委托密函免费获得/商店购买获得。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-XESRda7E2oulPRxFUgqcDHQcnNb\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-BIFQdC3uNof0N3xZeBOcgOkwn8e\">雷属性&middot;「煜明」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ICLQdx7GQomUvuxAk0McogHhnWb\">✦ 武器精通：长柄/突击枪</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PoZfd8dPMoGqIGxaiYvcoAF3nde\">✦ 获取开放时间：3月10日 10:00（UTC+8）后长期开放；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-FBZDdkpgYobeJOxqo2UcfsIBnhg\">✦ 获取方式：委托密函免费获得/商店购买获得。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnF87H7S8tsIQ7OR0Ytlp90g\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnJfv4VdnDucli8daPgTwLtb\"><strong>◆全新武器◆</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VEr0d5IgloDyFLxPyDDcd6kWn4e\">重剑&middot;「万古的诀别」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-NamOdAgTJokeT1xPJXUcmvyznGg\">✦ 获取方式：通过铸造免费获得/通过商店购买获得；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PIB5dLuySoPZpkxWbOlc18OJnxc\">✦ 获取开放时间：2月10日（UTC+8）更新后长期开放；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Zgo6dMmOCoHGTLx5AoKcVSNsnnd\">*「密函：万古的诀别」通过当期沉浸式戏剧【观剧纪念】商店购买获得。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-YHmWdUHQaoWf95xnrdnc7psjnWe\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-LMvRdsJ6ioAFYcxwggpc3ujbnmc\">双刀&middot;「风云决」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Tc5bd6Pz5octx8xRKArcQbdSnUb\">✦ 获取方式：通过铸造免费获得/通过商店购买获得；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ByObdxjlLog74lxCtQfctXl5nHb\">✦ 获取开放时间：2月10日（UTC+8）更新后长期开放；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-WJwVdppW1ogm2sxoF77clbO8nEI\">*「密函：风云决」通过梦魇残声获得。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EM2HdAl1koiTKoxLdAkcGKQ8n8f\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-D8M5dk6g1oM9eAxv44AcAc99nBc\">长柄&middot;「罪愆的逆鳞」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ATyHdlWODoiIW1xsZuwcOlosnRe\">✦ 获取方式：通过铸造免费获得/通过商店购买获得；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-X6nYdL7DTopeaIx9